727624f-b.title: Queens: Northern Boulevard - 162nd Street
727624f-b.text:
Northern Boulevard, at the N.E. corner of 162nd Street,
showing the local office--known as the Broadway-Flushing
office--of the Rickert-Finlay Real Estate Company, when this
neighborhood was still sparsely settled. The tracks are of
the North Shore Division of the Long lIsland Railroad. When
these photographs were taken Northern Boulevard, here, was
called Broadway, hence the designation ''Broadway-Flushing''
for the company's local office.
MAY BE REPRODUCED  About 1900
Views 1,2
